        {
            "id": "http://example.com/2021/03/12/iOS%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6/",
            "url": "http://example.com/2021/03/12/iOS%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6/",
            "title": "iOS多线程数据安全控制",
            "date_published": "2021-03-12T06:16:47.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>在项目工程中我们难免遇到多线程数据读写的操作，很多时候多线程读写数据需要满足多读单写的要求，我们在开发过程中可以通过使用读写锁 —— <strong>pthread_rwlock_t</strong> 来进行实现。</p>\n<h4 id=\"引入所需要的头文件\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#引入所需要的头文件\">#</a> 引入所需要的头文件</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight objc\"><figcaption data-lang=\"objc\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>pthread<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>h<span class=\"token operator\">></span></span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"初始化读写锁对象\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#初始化读写锁对象\">#</a> 初始化读写锁对象</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight objc\"><figcaption data-lang=\"objc\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">pthread_rwlock_init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>_testLock<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token constant\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">// 初始化读写锁 testLock</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"读取操作加锁与解锁\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#读取操作加锁与解锁\">#</a> \u0003读取操作加锁与解锁</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight objc\"><figcaption data-lang=\"objc\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>read <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre> \t<span class=\"token function\">pthread_rwlock_rdlock</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>_testLock<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">// 加锁</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre> \t<span class=\"token function\">NSLog</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">@\"读取\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre> \t<span class=\"token function\">pthread_rwlock_unlock</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>_testLock<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">// 解锁</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"写入操作的加锁与解锁\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#写入操作的加锁与解锁\">#</a> 写入操作的加锁与解锁</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight objc\"><figcaption data-lang=\"objc\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>write <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token function\">pthread_rwlock_wrlock</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>_testLock<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">// 加锁</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre> \t<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre> \t\t<span class=\"token function\">NSLog</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">@\"写入%d\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre> \t\t<span class=\"token function\">sleep</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token function\">pthread_rwlock_unlock</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>_testLock<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">// 解锁</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>经过以上的操作后就可以实现多读单写，多个线程可以同时读取，但是一个时间之内只有一个线程能够写入。</p>\n",
            "tags": []
        },
